OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778785871
OL,3,CDrunk driver who crashed into traffic
OL,4,Clights banned from driving
OL,6,FWatch the moment a drink driver
OL,7,Fcrashes into traffic lights in
OL,8,FWiltshire.
OL,10,FA 73-year-old drink driver has been
OL,11,Fbanned from driving after crashing
OL,12,Finto a set of traffic lights in
OL,13,FTrowbridge.
OL,15,FGarrick Jones, from Bathwick, pled
OL,16,Fguilty to drink driving after
OL,17,Fattending court in April.
OL,19,FOn 11 May, he was given a 27-month
OL,20,Fdriving ban and ordered to carry out
OL,21,F80 hours of unpaid work.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
