PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778785871
OL,3,CDrunk driver who crashed into traffic
OL,4,Clights banned from driving
OL,6,FHe will also pay a #114 surcharge and
OL,7,F#85 fine to the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Frome Road in
OL,11,FTrowbridge on 31 March where a car had
OL,12,Fmounted the pavement, collided with
OL,13,Fmultiple vehicles and crashed into a
OL,14,Fset of traffic lights.
OL,16,FJones failed a roadside breath test
OL,17,Fand was later arrested and taken into
OL,18,Fcustody.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
