OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778785871
OL,3,CDrunk driver who crashed into traffic
OL,4,Clights banned from driving
OL,6,FPC Craig Beales, from Wiltshire's
OL,7,Froads policing unit, said: "This
OL,8,Fincident shows just how dangerous and
OL,9,Freckless drink driving is.
OL,11,F"It was only through sheer luck that
OL,12,Fno one was seriously injured when
OL,13,FJones' vehicle mounted the pavement
OL,14,Fand struck multiple cars and traffic
OL,15,Flights.
OL,17,F"Jones was found to be well over the
OL,18,Flimit following the collision and in
OL,19,Fnot fit state to be behind the wheel
OL,20,Fof a car.
OL,26,@oD@\OUyD@AOU
